12 (d) A taxpayer shall not be eligible for a homestead property tax
13 refund claim pursuant to this section if such taxpayer has received for
14 such property for such tax year either: (1) A homestead property tax
15 refund pursuant to K.S.A. 79-4508, and amendments thereto; or (2) the
16 selective assistance for effective senior relief (SAFESR) credit pursuant
17 to K.S.A. 79-32,263, and amendments thereto.
18 (e) The amount of any claim shall be computed to the nearest $1.
19 (f) The provisions of this section shall be a part of and
20 supplemental to the homestead property tax refund act.
